<div class="title">It's Not About Fun</div>
<div class="substance">AMT & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=G.+love&Exact=1">G. love</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; G. love. "It's Not About Fun: An Experience with AMT & Cannabis (exp17961)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 7, 2002. erowid.org/exp/17961</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
